OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781384335
OL,3,CTwo women arrested after man found
OL,4,Cdead in former restaurant
OL,6,FTwo women have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder after a man's body
OL,8,Fwas found in a former restaurant
OL,9,Fbuilding in Sheffield.
OL,11,FSouth Yorkshire Police were called to
OL,12,Freports of suspicious activity at the
OL,13,Fderelict building, which was formerly
OL,14,Fa TGI Fridays, on June 10.
OL,16,FThe body of a 55-year-old man was
OL,17,Ffound but he has not been formally
OL,18,Fidentified.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
