OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781384335
OL,3,CTwo women arrested after man found
OL,4,Cdead in former restaurant
OL,6,FThe next day, two women, aged 35 and
OL,7,F54, were arrested and remain in
OL,8,Fcustody.
OL,10,FOfficers said his family however has
OL,11,Fbeen informed and is being supported
OL,12,Fby officers.JDCI Laura Procter said
OL,13,Fhas urged anyone who may have
OL,14,Fwitnessed anything to come forward.
OL,16,F"Officers have been conducting various
OL,17,Fenquiries since the man's body was
OL,18,Fsadly found, with the aim of building
OL,19,Fup a full picture of the circumstances
OL,20,Fwhich led up to this incident.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
