CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781384335
OL,3,CTwo women arrested after man found
OL,4,Cdead in former restaurant
OL,6,F"I am particularly keen for anyone who
OL,7,Fmay have seen suspicious activity in
OL,8,Fthe area around the TGI Fridays
OL,9,Fbuilding in the days leading up to
OL,10,FWednesday, to get in touch with us,"
OL,11,Fshe added.
OL,13,FTGI Fridays has since moved to
OL,14,Fdistance itself from the building,
OL,15,Fclarifying that the Sheffield Road
OL,16,Fsite was closed in January 2026 and is
OL,17,F"no longer owned by the company or any
OL,18,Faffiliated organization."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
